originalText.text: Extremely rude, verbally abusive to my aunt who arrived 1 hour early for her appointment.  While her unprofessional staff directed my aunt to return at 2 pm for her 1 pm appointment because the doctor needed to have lunch and see three other patients.  The rant the doctor went on was a disgrace to the profession.. It is no wonder you only have one star. If I could give you zero stars I would.  Please take a manners class.
